import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'
import AdminSideBar from '../../Components/Admin/AdminSideBar'

export default function AdminAllProductPage() {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Row>
            <Col sm='2' md='3'>
              <AdminSideBar/>
            </Col>

            <Col sm='2' md='3'>
              <AdminAll/>
            </Col>
        </Row>
    </Container>
  )
}
